HTML Forms

HTML forms are used to send data to a server.

---

Form Tag

<form action="url" method="get">
</form>

---

Attributes

action  → where to send data
method="get"  → data goes in URL
method="post" → data goes in body
target  → where to show result

---

Input Types

Text: <input type="text">

Password: <input type="password">

Textarea:

<textarea></textarea>

---

Buttons

<input type="submit">
<input type="reset">
<input type="button">

---

